arts.ttl: Cristiano Ronaldo 'is open to LEAVING Al-Nassr' with Portuguese superstar allowed to negotiate a move to another club on January 1... but there is a key reason why he wants to stay in Saudi Arabia
arts.sum: Cristiano Ronaldo is reportedly open to leaving Al-Nassr , with his contract set to expire in the summer. From January 1 Ronaldo will be free to begin negotiating with other clubs.

arts.ttl: Preview: Oman vs. Saudi Arabia - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Tuesday's Gulf Cup of Nations clash between Oman and Saudi Arabia, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
